{"h7f12e361ga763g41acga1b4ga4c778a09183": ["*Apart from an overgrowth of moss, the well looks unremarkable.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_InteractWithWell.html", "30ef8488-f55a-4093-8df4-9bfdd7e39a52"], "ha3c643fag2090g4bb7gbd45g7ce30991f254": ["<i>Throw a coin into the well.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_InteractWithWell.html", "0df1cf04-fd74-bf53-d43f-a67665322255"], "h73e244d5g2d9fg40f6g9ca3g6232a15821ae": ["*The coin disappears into the darkness, landing with a soft <i>clink</i>.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_InteractWithWell.html", "4ef3dfaf-585a-0d99-6ba2-f26c19ee258c"], "h3e9ff28bg4915g424cg9cfeg11398536892e": ["*The coin disappears into the well. After a moment, you hear a soft <i>clink </i>- not a splash.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_InteractWithWell.html", "4f10c5a1-8b04-85ed-7f3a-fc1b2ff88751"], "h6e9476begef03g4140gb26fg241183abb5a3": ["<i>Peer into the well.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_InteractWithWell.html", "10440ba9-39c9-8489-75b1-76426b9be5a1"], "h6a445f1fg4cbfg447bgaf9ege12fdb79359f": ["*Dry stones line the wall. At the bottom, something gleams in the dappled light.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_InteractWithWell.html", "33b533fa-826d-5740-8f5a-7791ada8bd35"], "h43d68721gd896g4e56g9188g3b943552a0d3": ["<i>Climb down the bucket rope.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_InteractWithWell.html", "64bb783e-8a74-70af-4c56-f258216f6a1a"], "h9980d0d6g338fg467ag89d2g1e837da1e9d1": ["*Dry stones line the wall, but the darkness below is impenetrable.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_InteractWithWell.html", "406d14d5-b438-8d03-34f0-ac1bf6a62e62"], "hc6149c0bg2727g4631gb206g67892d2d6f4d": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_InteractWithWell.html", "c1f1bea8-68d1-8693-790b-e3989130f88c"], "hd92e7283gf9a2g4d60gad07g2cd420e8f2d1": ["*The well stands, as it has for ages.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_InteractWithWell.html", "f705d706-477f-5b2a-6b33-7b55a1f23910"], "hbefc41c4g0d59g4cd1g9462g276173b4c629": ["*The well doesn't look too deep, and the old bucket rope feels strong enough.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_InteractWithWell.html", "5e044c12-b2ad-d4fb-df77-7762d7cb6903"]}